<% content_for :head do %>
    <%= stylesheet_link_tag "widget" %>
<% end %>

<div class="wl-content-container" id="widget_container">
    <div id="widget_download">
        <img src="../images/widget_small_preview.jpg" alt="<%= @widget %> preview">
        <a target="_blank" class="wl-button wl-header-button" href="#">Download</a>
    </div>
    <div id="widget_description">
        <h1 class="wl-bold">Activity Plus <span id="widget_version">v3.0</span></h1>
        by <a href="#" title="James Johnson" class="wl-regular-link">James Johnson</a>
        <p>A+ adds additional functionality to an already popular Sakai widget. Just few taps and your activity chart is ready. You can save it for later or email immediately.</p>
        <ul>
            <li>supports rotation,</li>
            <li>add new slices (up to 12),</li>
            <li>move slices on a chart in slice settings,</li>
            <li>change slice size,</li>
            <li>rotate whole chart, just swipe your finger next to chart border,</li>
            <li>skew and scale chart in real time,</li>
            <li>save for later, in chart settings, chart is saved with date and chart name.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
</div>